name: Nymphelis Cubixta
description: “This specimen was originated by fusing the radiosynthesis feeding system with blockchain algorithms. This butterfly can crawl into the internet to find its nearest source of radiation on the cosmos.” – Cosmic Butterfly Collection series 3 - This is a digitally developed art. Originally painted on its negative colors on paper using watercolor technique. This limited edition of the reveled piece is 5446x4558 px, 28.1MB, painted in 140lb cold pressed cotton paper by Adilson Matioli.
